casebody.data:
BRIDGEPORT DENTAL, LLC
v.
COMMISSIONER OF SOCIAL SERVICES. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 29, 2016.

Jonathan J. Klein, Bridgeport, in support of the petition.

Robert B. Teitelman, assistant attorney general, in opposition.

The plaintiff's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 165 Conn.App. 642, 140 A.3d 263 (2016), is denied.
